Date: Fri, 1 Jun 2018 11:46:08 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Input: xpad - add GPD Win 2 Controller USB IDs
References: bnc#1012382
Patch-mainline: 4.4.166
Git-commit: c1ba08390a8bb13c927e699330896adc15b78205

